<h1 id="启用root账户及密码自动验证">启用root账户及密码自动验证</h1>
<ol>
  <li>使用Google Cloud网页版ssh，切换到root
    <div class="language-shell highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="nb">sudo</span> <span class="nt">-i</span>  
</code></pre></div>    </div>
  </li>
  <li>编辑ssh配置文件
    <div class="language-shell highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>vi /etc/ssh/sshd_config  
</code></pre></div>    </div>
  </li>
  <li>修改以下的内容
    <div class="language-shell highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>PermitRootLogin <span class="nb">yes
</span>PasswordAuthentication <span class="nb">yes</span>
</code></pre></div>    </div>
    <!--more-->
    <p><img src="http://localhost:4000/assets/blogImg/2018/google_cloud_ssh/google_cloud_ssh_01.png" alt="" /></p>
  </li>
  <li>重启ssh
    <div class="language-shell highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>service sshd restart
</code></pre></div>    </div>
  </li>
</ol>

<h1 id="修改当前账户和root账户的密码">修改当前账户和root账户的密码</h1>
<ol>
  <li>设置当前账户新密码
    <div class="language-shell highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="nb">sudo </span>passwd <span class="k">${</span><span class="nv">whoami</span><span class="k">}</span> 
</code></pre></div>    </div>
    <!--more-->
  </li>
  <li>设置root账户新密码
    <div class="language-shell highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="nb">sudo </span>passwd root
</code></pre></div>    </div>
    <p><img src="http://localhost:4000/assets/blogImg/2018/google_cloud_ssh/google_cloud_ssh_02.png" alt="" /></p>
  </li>
</ol>

